'''卡爾馬城堡'''（{{lang-sv|Kalmar slott}}）是位於[[瑞典|瑞典]]城市[[卡爾馬|卡爾馬]]的一座城堡建築<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sfv.se/cms/sfv/english/holiday/Kalmar_Castle.html |title=''Kalmar Castle'' (Statens fastighetsverk) |accessdate=2016-01-16 |archive-date=2011-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110612083210/http://www.sfv.se/cms/sfv/english/holiday/Kalmar_Castle.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。卡爾馬城堡始建於12世紀。1397年，卡爾馬聯盟在此成立<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://staff.kings.edu/bapavlac/knightsandcastles/kalmar.html |title=''Kalmar Castle'' (Castle of the Day) |accessdate=2016-01-16 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304235916/http://staff.kings.edu/bapavlac/knightsandcastles/kalmar.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此後卡爾馬城堡年久失修。1856年，卡爾馬城堡開始重建。現在卡爾馬城堡是瑞典保存狀態最好的重建城堡之一，對普通公眾開放<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.smithsonianmag.com/specialsections/ricksteves/Kalmar-Castle-Swedens-Royal-Hub.html |title=''Kalmar Castle: Sweden’s Royal Hub'' (Smithsonian Institution) |accessdate=2016-01-16 |archive-date=2013-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203020401/http://www.smithsonianmag.com/specialsections/ricksteves/Kalmar-Castle-Swedens-Royal-Hub.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
